3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses self-supervised learning techniques. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with learning from data without ground-truth labels, which is a common problem in AI. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with photometric consistency and image sequences, which are relevant to graphics applications.
